rmed-by-netflix-3341500"><em>《睡魔》</em></a> ，后来被改编成 Netflix 剧集。</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系盖曼的代表征求意见。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sprints-karla-chubb-interview-girls-against-groping-gigs-assault-3752440"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harvey-weinsteins-2020-rape-conviction-overturned-by-new-york-court-3750698"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p><strong>如需有关英国性骚扰、侵犯和强奸的更多帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="http://rapecrisis.org.uk/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> 。</strong></p></div></div></div></div><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/neil-gaiman-accused-of-sexual-assault-by-two-women-3771826">尼尔·盖曼被指控性侵两名女性的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
